body  that  drives  down  a  back  road  in  the  Sierra  Nevadas  is  being
exposed.

Mr. CAMPLIN. Well, it is the State mineral of California.
Mr.  BILBRAY.  Yeah.  Well,  I  guess  it  is  appropriate  with  our  air
