Panel II:

Chair  MILLER.  I  would  like  to  introduce  our  second  panel.  Dr.
Ronnie  Wilson,  in  addition  to  being  a  former  country  music  disc
jockey  as  he  told  me  in  the  break,  probably  more  pertinent  to  this
